data.description: MOVE-IN READY, must see to appreciate!  This home would be perfect for starter home, investment unit or retirement home situated on an interior lot.  This charmer is a 3-bedroom split floor plan with 1.5 baths, nice open living area with coat closet and ceiling fan, window treatments, appliances, large utility room, guttering as well as asphalt roof replaced in 2017.  The master bedroom has the half bath and the 3rd bedroom off the utility area would make a great office for those who work from home.  The home has central gas heat and electric air system.  Very little carpet in this house as the majority is wood laminate and tile flooring.  The owner is also conveying the exterior storage building located at the back of the lot which is accessible by the rear alley.  This would also make it easy to have an extra parking area in the back of the home on this roomy lot.
